---
title: Middle Eastern-Inspired Bison Calzones with Tomato-Cucumber Salad
description: Treat yourself to these crispy, creamy, cheesy calzones, packed with all the spicy, umami goodness that poblanos and bison have to offer! A tomato-cucumber salad on the side provides bursts of freshness in between bites of these perfectly delicious pockets.
